				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "You get a telepathing message from the elder brain if you killed Gortash before killing Orin. This dialog starts right after the combat wil Gortash ends.\r\nIf the foundry hasn't been destroyed yet, the brain promises to take care of it.\r\nThe brain also rassures the palyer that they will take care of any witnesses to the palyer killing Gortash.\r\nThe Brain instructs the palyer to kill Orin."
